6. Execution engine loop

Here’s the actual canonical loop:

Sense
  -> Encode
  -> Transform across bases
  -> Detect patterns
  -> Generate interpretations
  -> Rank actions
  -> Reflect/store delta

More concretely:

User logs shoulder tension + poor sleep
-> semantic basis creates multiple summaries
-> math basis computes trend + graph links
-> science basis infers catalyst / load / reactivity
-> Hound flags recurrence
-> Conductor ranks likely interventions
-> EchoFrame stores distilled pattern

That is an execution engine.

